{
  "stem": "26728.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And another one up on the roof of a-- of a building across the street.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And in-- inside of this wall are these SS guys, 30, 40 of them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And these two squads are just shooting them down, mowing them down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And there's pictures in there of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So I thought, Jesus, you know, I could stop this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I was a first lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These-- and I couldn't tell who the other, the rank of these.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could see one guy with sergeant stripes on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a crew of four or five around each gun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ammunition, you know, and these are those machine guns that you feed with a belt, 30 caliber.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they-- then I saw an inmate jump over the wall with a 45.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he goes over, and anybody that's still alive, he shoots them in the head.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Three or four-- three or four guys were still alive, I guess.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he just pops them in the head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there's pictures of that in there too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't know what the hell to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I thought, you know, this is a war crime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And these thoughts went through my mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I didn't-- I wasn't saying we can't do this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't feel-- I didn't feel-- and I've thought about this a lot-- I didn't feel like I should stop it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I wasn't sure I could stop it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I wasn't sure that if I did try that this guy wouldn't shoot me too, because they were nuts.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then they brought out some more guys from the hospital, from what I found out later was the hospital, 30, 40.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there's-- there's dead guy's laying there, and they lined them all up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And these two squads shot-- finished them off.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
